import React from "react"
import Link from "next/link"
import {BlogLink, RightNavStyled} from './header_styled'
import {Icon} from "../utils/icons/icon"

const RightNav = () => (
	<RightNavStyled>
		<Link href="/contact">
			<BlogLink>Contact</BlogLink>
			<Icon icon="GithubIcon" />
		</Link>
	</RightNavStyled>
)

export default RightNav
